Marcus joined Basalt in 2015 and is located in the London office. Marcus advises on the origination, execution, management and operation of investments, predominately in Western Europe. Previously, Marcus spent nearly three years in financial modelling where most recently he was a Transaction Modelling Executive at EY. Marcus has a wealth of modelling experience, having also worked on a number of infrastructure mandates. Marcus has over three years of corporate finance experience of which a significant part has been within infrastructure. Marcus holds a BSc in Management from the University of Warwick.



