About Us | Basalt


































 Home / About Us
 






Basalt Infrastructure Partners LLP (Basalt) is an independent infrastructure investment firm, with a transatlantic focus on mid market infrastructure.
Who we are:

Infrastructure investment firm focused on the mid market
Dedicated team of experienced investment professionals

What we do:

Provide investment advisory services to Basalt Infrastructure Partners LLP
Key sectors of focus include energy, transport and utilities

Why we are different:

Strategy to deliver enhanced returns by bringing together:

Advisory and investment management skills of experienced investment professionals



The Team:

Dedicated team of infrastructure investment professionals with proven track record

Where we are located:

Basalt and its affiliates operate across Europe and North America
Basalt team based in London, Munich and New York


































