Notices published in the Gazette
17 Jul 2017
LIMITED PARTNERSHIPS ACT 1907
Notice is hereby given, pursuant to section 10 of the Limited
Partnerships Act 1907, that on 1 July 2017, Massachusetts Mutual
Life Insurance Company (the "Transferor") transferred part of its
interest including a capital contribution of £175, held by it in Basalt
Infrastructure Partners L.P. (the "Partnership"), a limited partnership
registered in England with number LP015216, to MassMutual Trad
Private Equity LLC (the "Transferee") and that with effect from 1 July
2017, the Transferee became limited partner in the Partnership, the
Transferor reduced its capital contribution in the Partnership by
£175.00 and the Transferee increased its capital contribution in the
Partnership by £175.
Basalt Infrastructure Partners GP Limited
For and on behalf of Basalt Infrastrucure Partners, L.P.
30 June 2017
Source Document

6 Jul 2016
LIMITED PARTNERSHIPS ACT 1907
Notice is hereby given, pursuant to section 10 of the Limited
Partnerships Act 1907, that on 30 June 2016 Balfour Beatty
Infrastructure Investments Limited transferred to Wafra Cornerstone
GP Ltd as general partner on behalf of Wafra Cornerstone Partners
GP, LP as general partner on behalf of CP Bay Holdings LP all of the
interest held by it in Balfour Beatty Infrastructure Partners L.P. (the
“Partnership”), a limited partnership registered in England with
number LP015216 and that with effect from 30 June 2016 Balfour
Beatty Infrastructure Investments Limited ceased to be a limited
partner and Wafra Cornerstone GP Ltd as general partner on behalf of
Wafra Cornerstone Partners GP, LP as general partner on behalf of
CP Bay Holdings LP became a limited partner in the Partnership.
NOTICE OF CHANGE OF PARTNER
